{"tid":148173,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"7粒fair骰仔既機率問題","createTime":"2017-03-08T11:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T04:34:15.000Z","uid":3258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3bddc53e557877c1aa1c1f39ce1c726d831d227c","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:36:00.000Z","msg":"岩岩諗左幾個同驚有關既機率問題<br />\n點知同fd諗爆頭都諗唔到<br />\n有冇巴絲打得閒可以show下點計個機率<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先手上就有7粒機率均等既骰仔<br />\n<br />\n全部擲出去<br />\n係唔強求順次序（即係出黎個結果可以任郁）<br />\n<br />\n1）有4連number（如1234）/以上（即含5 6連）既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n2）有兩pair 2個（1111都叫兩pair)同number既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n3)有2pair 3個同number既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n特別係連number 個度 因為第7粒骰仔存在搞到諗極諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ac9b7d166d083fc338447dffce4c3ba401c42a","tid":148173,"uid":60733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652adbbc40328c1b562d2d3557aace0d22334fc5","tid":148173,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6223801162512f9ab83c3b95ce965a74c727e6b","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1) 1/7*1/7*1/7*1/7<br />\n<br />\n利申9up</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 數學大師"},{"pid":"555fb54b293adba6e160af7aa31ad363d5ad3ea8","tid":148173,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩諗左幾個同驚有關既機率問題<br />\n點知同fd諗爆頭都諗唔到<br />\n有冇巴絲打得閒可以show下點計個機率<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先手上就有7粒機率均等既骰仔<br />\n<br />\n全部擲出去<br />\n係唔強求順次序（即係出黎個結果可以任郁）<br />\n<br />\n1）有4連number（如1234）/以上（即含5 6連）既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n2）有兩pair 2個（1111都叫兩pair)同number既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n3)有2pair 3個同number既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n特別係連number 個度 因為第7粒骰仔存在搞到諗極諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一個數哂所有可能性出嚟咪得<br />\n唔會好難"},{"pid":"578cf42952647957d68114602099518bad960a21","tid":148173,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:42:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bbfaa1c937367c7cd346b6f29954729ff823aad","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩諗左幾個同驚有關既機率問題<br />\n點知同fd諗爆頭都諗唔到<br />\n有冇巴絲打得閒可以show下點計個機率<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先手上就有7粒機率均等既骰仔<br />\n<br />\n全部擲出去<br />\n係唔強求順次序（即係出黎個結果可以任郁）<br />\n<br />\n1）有4連number（如1234）/以上（即含5 6連）既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n2）有兩pair 2個（1111都叫兩pair)同number既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n3)有2pair 3個同number既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n特別係連number 個度 因為第7粒骰仔存在搞到諗極諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一個數哂所有可能性出嚟咪得<br />\n唔會好難</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁做法 會唔會太古老"},{"pid":"2a66dbb7c5b6bbf673e6eaf159a20b0b3ee4fe8d","tid":148173,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>岩岩諗左幾個同驚有關既機率問題<br />\n點知同fd諗爆頭都諗唔到<br />\n有冇巴絲打得閒可以show下點計個機率<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先手上就有7粒機率均等既骰仔<br />\n<br />\n全部擲出去<br />\n係唔強求順次序（即係出黎個結果可以任郁）<br />\n<br />\n1）有4連number（如1234）/以上（即含5 6連）既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n2）有兩pair 2個（1111都叫兩pair)同number既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n3)有2pair 3個同number既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n特別係連number 個度 因為第7粒骰仔存在搞到諗極諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一個數哂所有可能性出嚟咪得<br />\n唔會好難</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁做法 會唔會太古老</blockquote><br />\n可能數得systematically少少嘅，但都快唔得幾多"},{"pid":"a3d1ab83e132b61ddc4fd0580e5a5e66a0246c87","tid":148173,"uid":2896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:11:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩諗左幾個同驚有關既機率問題<br />\n點知同fd諗爆頭都諗唔到<br />\n有冇巴絲打得閒可以show下點計個機率<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先手上就有7粒機率均等既骰仔<br />\n<br />\n全部擲出去<br />\n係唔強求順次序（即係出黎個結果可以任郁）<br />\n<br />\n1）有4連number（如1234）/以上（即含5 6連）既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n2）有兩pair 2個（1111都叫兩pair)同number既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n3)有2pair 3個同number既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n特別係連number 個度 因為第7粒骰仔存在搞到諗極諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1) 7C4x(1/6)^(4) x(5/6)^(3)+7C5x(1/6)^(5)x(5/6)^(2)+7C6x(1/6)^(6)x(5/6)+7C7x(1/6)^7<br />\n有錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f9455d043ebf9c49ee53cb4da4699cd7e0f4a5","tid":148173,"uid":2896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:15:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩諗左幾個同驚有關既機率問題<br />\n點知同fd諗爆頭都諗唔到<br />\n有冇巴絲打得閒可以show下點計個機率<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先手上就有7粒機率均等既骰仔<br />\n<br />\n全部擲出去<br />\n係唔強求順次序（即係出黎個結果可以任郁）<br />\n<br />\n1）有4連number（如1234）/以上（即含5 6連）既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n2）有兩pair 2個（1111都叫兩pair)同number既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n3)有2pair 3個同number既機率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n特別係連number 個度 因為第7粒骰仔存在搞到諗極諗唔到<br />\n<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1) 7C4x(1/6)^(4) x(5/6)^(3)+7C5x(1/6)^(5)x(5/6)^(2)+7C6x(1/6)^(6)x(5/6)<br />\n有錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眼殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca5ca4df08beb0637b09ccf0225b00ded874270","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:20:17.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=7+dice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolframalpha.com%2Finput%2F%3Fi%3D7%2Bdice&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=34035b27\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=7+dice</a><br />\n其實至少6連我係搵到大概9%左右<br />\n(表入面all faces show 即係1-6出哂,即係達成6連)<br />\n<br />\n所以用依個我發現我諗個d(抽6連個part黎計)都唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98927957c93133091eefe3691caca10349d8c5be","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:20:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=7+dice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolframalpha.com%2Finput%2F%3Fi%3D7%2Bdice&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=34035b27\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=7+dice</a><br />\n其實至少6連我係搵到大概<span style=\"color: red;\">5%</span>左右<br />\n(表入面all faces show 即係1-6出哂,即係達成6連)<br />\n<br />\n所以用依個我發現我諗個d(抽6連個part黎計)都唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e42c1df71dde56761c1b7d330399b0025db92d5a","tid":148173,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:22:23.000Z","msg":"最簡單嘅做法應該係類似咁：<br />\n首先數<br />\n1234xxx<br />\n有幾多個可能性（只可以係444、445等等）<br />\n再乘返7!<br />\n之後再睇x1234xx, 如此類推<br />\n不過到2345就要小心有冇再之前1234嗰啲重覆"},{"pid":"e790c3b45ded408301bb72824c7cc93915518076","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最簡單嘅做法應該係類似咁：<br />\n首先數<br />\n1234xxx<br />\n有幾多個可能性（只可以係444、445等等）<br />\n再乘返7!<br />\n之後再睇x1234xx, 如此類推<br />\n不過到2345就要小心有冇再之前1234嗰啲重覆</blockquote><br />\n咁攞命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0621113da9cd8047d2adafd508731115b96bafc5","tid":148173,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最簡單嘅做法應該係類似咁：<br />\n首先數<br />\n1234xxx<br />\n有幾多個可能性（<span style=\"color: red;\">只可以係444、445等等）</span><br />\n再乘返7!<br />\n之後再睇x1234xx, 如此類推<br />\n不過到2345就要小心有冇再之前1234嗰啲重覆</blockquote><br />\n諗諗吓應該可以包埋其他組合，唔當佢順序<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就唔需要睇x1234xx之類<br />\n不過到2345開始就好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345b855384480bd173602bccf9509651362aa779","tid":148173,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=7+dice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolframalpha.com%2Finput%2F%3Fi%3D7%2Bdice&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=34035b27\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=7+dice</a><br />\n其實至少6連我係搵到大概9%左右<br />\n(表入面all faces show 即係1-6出哂,即係達成6連)<br />\n<br />\n所以用依個我發現我諗個d(抽6連個part黎計)都唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n6連就易計少少<br />\n用返頭先個方法<br />\n首先計123456x有幾多個可能<br />\n咁x只能夠就1 2 3 4 5 6<br />\n所以得6個可能<br />\n再乘返7!就係所有可能嘅permutations<br />\n但由於有兩粒骰數字一樣，所以有一半其實係重覆咗，所以要除以2(啱啱發覺漏咗呢點)<br />\n<br />\n個prob就係 6x7!/(2x6^7)"},{"pid":"a449595e32846b85d927b7f71b3bf351f2544667","tid":148173,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:57:04.000Z","msg":"btw 2, 3你係問緊conditional probability定乜？睇唔太明"},{"pid":"a8d2e3fbc97cbb5b2049ae7a5987027388638e30","tid":148173,"uid":85839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:06:14.000Z","msg":"呢d情況未必可以好簡單咁計到<br />\n始終要有系統咁加哂d情況"},{"pid":"99cc7c2cda2a9b5f3a83d5cdef4192cf81a8fd7d","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw 2, 3你係問緊conditional probability定乜？睇唔太明</blockquote><br />\n2,3黎講<br />\n<br />\n例如你<br />\n11 22  345<br />\n咁樣,11 22已經出現2pair 2個同數字咁樣<br />\n而11 23456<br />\n得1pair 唔符合情況<br />\n<br />\n11 11 234<br />\n都符合2pair同數字咁"},{"pid":"8fb4b23a95a4b0a7898ab6e9896c898543b4e9c9","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:15:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d情況未必可以好簡單咁計到<br />\n始終要有系統咁加哂d情況</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁睇黎要放棄"},{"pid":"42b1e909b72ae3a808885f200213b3b63d76e33d","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"連no冇咩可能計到出黎<br />\n<br />\n咁pair有冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e5e9fe6271ad1da96f57f3ff5e569c44dcbc30","tid":148173,"uid":58090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:41:55.000Z","msg":"求其試下permutations cxxxxxxxxtion 唔得咩"},{"pid":"294983c0d023582f5ccc06a8194064f5b36c1d9b","tid":148173,"uid":89729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"用factorial去諗啦<br />\n用C定P呢d其實好死"},{"pid":"de2f1002f6c26b811e4b2920a4b2e05ceb360684","tid":148173,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>btw 2, 3你係問緊conditional probability定乜？睇唔太明</blockquote><br />\n2,3黎講<br />\n<br />\n例如你<br />\n11 22  345<br />\n咁樣,11 22已經出現2pair 2個同數字咁樣<br />\n而11 23456<br />\n得1pair 唔符合情況<br />\n<br />\n11 11 234<br />\n都符合2pair同數字咁</blockquote><br />\n3 pair符唔符合？"},{"pid":"c9f5bc797de97a206978f17e33e4be90cc7a7cb5","tid":148173,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:54:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連no冇咩可能計到出黎<br />\n<br />\n咁pair有冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\npair易好多<br />\n例如3，個probability係<br />\n(7C3 x 6) x (4C3 x 6) x 6 / 6^7<br />\n<br />\n第一個括號係7粒是但揀3粒<br />\n嗰3粒要同一個數字，有6個可能性<br />\n<br />\n第二個就係淨低嗰4粒是但揀3粒<br />\n如此類推"},{"pid":"b84d1f6e634920cd21c53b07e3f24cf5b35c4473","tid":148173,"uid":47084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:05:38.000Z","msg":"有冇答案啊"},{"pid":"cb0a1ce599fb12c3b0535be63a4bbd3fec212584","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:11:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>btw 2, 3你係問緊conditional probability定乜？睇唔太明</blockquote><br />\n2,3黎講<br />\n<br />\n例如你<br />\n11 22  345<br />\n咁樣,11 22已經出現2pair 2個同數字咁樣<br />\n而11 23456<br />\n得1pair 唔符合情況<br />\n<br />\n11 11 234<br />\n都符合2pair同數字咁</blockquote><br />\n3 pair符唔符合？</blockquote><br />\n3pair都符合<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e75062697b05ab53b54fc5c8be538889d2b57dc","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:11:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇答案啊</blockquote><br />\n其實冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...."},{"pid":"7f2825f376b8a11e850e0a3a2f6812d1acf780a5","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:26:03.000Z","msg":"列出全部可能性好似可以用EXCEL 列出黎<br />\n<br />\n之後用VLOOKUP之類好似可以SEARCH齊1234,2345個D連NO,再將數量加埋乘7! 再 / 總數就OK<br />\n<br />\n不過唔識點樣全列<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d6516c301e612bb9b3b7913b3e39a53aafa421","tid":148173,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>btw 2, 3你係問緊conditional probability定乜？睇唔太明</blockquote><br />\n2,3黎講<br />\n<br />\n例如你<br />\n11 22  345<br />\n咁樣,11 22已經出現2pair 2個同數字咁樣<br />\n而11 23456<br />\n得1pair 唔符合情況<br />\n<br />\n11 11 234<br />\n都符合2pair同數字咁</blockquote><br />\n3 pair符唔符合？</blockquote><br />\n3pair都符合<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁同3計法差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6afee700853b2740e63247a480206056bb7e8eb8","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"講返第1個問題<br />\n連number個度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuu.sh%2FuzJJf%2F42324964f6.csv&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a975b9d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv</a><br />\n首先呢,就用個excel檔列哂全部可能性(加埋有279936個)<br />\n<br />\n再ctrl+f 搜尋 1234, 2345, 3456 (4連既話得依3個可能性,5,6連已經包4連)<br />\n<br />\n1234,2345,3456 各出現846次<br />\n846*3 = 2538<br />\n<br />\n咁之後再將2538 * 4!<br />\n因為要考慮我地用ctrl+f 冇搵到,佢地次序打亂左(例如1234變2341)既可能性<br />\n<br />\n咁即係60912<br />\n<br />\n最後結果就係60912/279936<br />\n<br />\n=0.2222222222<br />\n<br />\n睇落個機率都幾合理<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53da2beed1d836e1a0581657a2168312e25c143e","tid":148173,"uid":35829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講返第1個問題<br />\n連number個度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuu.sh%2FuzJJf%2F42324964f6.csv&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a975b9d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv</a><br />\n首先呢,就用個excel檔列哂全部可能性(加埋有279936個)<br />\n<br />\n再ctrl+f 搜尋 1234, 2345, 3456 (4連既話得依3個可能性,5,6連已經包4連)<br />\n<br />\n1234,2345,3456 各出現846次<br />\n846*3 = 2538<br />\n<br />\n咁之後再將2538 * 4!<br />\n因為要考慮我地用ctrl+f 冇搵到,佢地次序打亂左(例如1234變2341)既可能性<br />\n<br />\n咁即係60912<br />\n<br />\n最後結果就係60912/279936<br />\n<br />\n=0.2222222222<br />\n<br />\n睇落個機率都幾合理<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1623444唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話唔考慮次序呀嘛<br />\n咁你ctrl f咪miss咗呢啲"},{"pid":"a44f3e5ccd22bcc49279d4fa56fa7837b82f4fe5","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:54:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講返第1個問題<br />\n連number個度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuu.sh%2FuzJJf%2F42324964f6.csv&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a975b9d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv</a><br />\n首先呢,就用個excel檔列哂全部可能性(加埋有279936個)<br />\n<br />\n再ctrl+f 搜尋 1234, 2345, 3456 (4連既話得依3個可能性,5,6連已經包4連)<br />\n<br />\n1234,2345,3456 各出現846次<br />\n846*3 = 2538<br />\n<br />\n咁之後再將2538 * 4!<br />\n因為要考慮我地用ctrl+f 冇搵到,佢地次序打亂左(例如1234變2341)既可能性<br />\n<br />\n咁即係60912<br />\n<br />\n最後結果就係60912/279936<br />\n<br />\n=0.2222222222<br />\n<br />\n睇落個機率都幾合理<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1623444唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話唔考慮次序呀嘛<br />\n咁你ctrl f咪miss咗呢啲</blockquote><br />\n1623444依種,用1234既數量乘左 4! 之後就包埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係(其實唔sure...)"},{"pid":"cdb9b7fcdc9059d7a9054868dddb1e176c9b9e16","tid":148173,"uid":35829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講返第1個問題<br />\n連number個度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuu.sh%2FuzJJf%2F42324964f6.csv&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a975b9d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv</a><br />\n首先呢,就用個excel檔列哂全部可能性(加埋有279936個)<br />\n<br />\n再ctrl+f 搜尋 1234, 2345, 3456 (4連既話得依3個可能性,5,6連已經包4連)<br />\n<br />\n1234,2345,3456 各出現846次<br />\n846*3 = 2538<br />\n<br />\n咁之後再將2538 * 4!<br />\n因為要考慮我地用ctrl+f 冇搵到,佢地次序打亂左(例如1234變2341)既可能性<br />\n<br />\n咁即係60912<br />\n<br />\n最後結果就係60912/279936<br />\n<br />\n=0.2222222222<br />\n<br />\n睇落個機率都幾合理<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1623444唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話唔考慮次序呀嘛<br />\n咁你ctrl f咪miss咗呢啲</blockquote><br />\n1623444依種,用1234既數量乘左 4! 之後就包埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係(其實唔sure...)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4! 係包左1234自己排位咋嘛 例如係<br />\n1234555<br />\n1342555<br />\n4123555<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n但係唔會包左<br />\n1555234架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4171fbbdd0367ddadf29e39289bc2b7946fb3e","tid":148173,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難，諗諗先"},{"pid":"65e7dc107ef53da794958ce3f3435021066e54f5","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:59:27.000Z","msg":"自膠..睇黎依招唔得<br />\n因為1234561<br />\n我search 1234,2345,3456都會出現<br />\n即係double(其實係triple) counting左...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bca8fce33169302dcfda1e06fcb300db5aacc82","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:00:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難，諗諗先</blockquote><br />\n其實4連number依個睇黎點都冇得計<br />\n但家下好似list哂可能性出黎都冇得咁容易暴力拆解..."},{"pid":"0a995fd68de0574cbc876f3227d15cd26f0356e8","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講返第1個問題<br />\n連number個度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuu.sh%2FuzJJf%2F42324964f6.csv&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a975b9d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv</a><br />\n首先呢,就用個excel檔列哂全部可能性(加埋有279936個)<br />\n<br />\n再ctrl+f 搜尋 1234, 2345, 3456 (4連既話得依3個可能性,5,6連已經包4連)<br />\n<br />\n1234,2345,3456 各出現846次<br />\n846*3 = 2538<br />\n<br />\n咁之後再將2538 * 4!<br />\n因為要考慮我地用ctrl+f 冇搵到,佢地次序打亂左(例如1234變2341)既可能性<br />\n<br />\n咁即係60912<br />\n<br />\n最後結果就係60912/279936<br />\n<br />\n=0.2222222222<br />\n<br />\n睇落個機率都幾合理<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1623444唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話唔考慮次序呀嘛<br />\n咁你ctrl f咪miss咗呢啲</blockquote><br />\n1623444依種,用1234既數量乘左 4! 之後就包埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係(其實唔sure...)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4! 係包左1234自己排位咋嘛 例如係<br />\n1234555<br />\n1342555<br />\n4123555<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n但係唔會包左<br />\n1555234架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但乘7!既話個分子會大過個分母(岩岩發現我依個方法避唔到double counting問題,所以846依個數應該錯)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我再諗諗..."},{"pid":"25b70b412b764e9fd2488de2d4c420dd78c7bd2b","tid":148173,"uid":35829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"1) 應該係107520 / 279936 = 38.41%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5458de55f03c9d79128e53a803a812e1f38ee59d","tid":148173,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:32:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講返第1個問題<br />\n連number個度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuu.sh%2FuzJJf%2F42324964f6.csv&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a975b9d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv</a><br />\n首先呢,就用個excel檔列哂全部可能性(加埋有279936個)<br />\n<br />\n再ctrl+f 搜尋 1234, 2345, 3456 (4連既話得依3個可能性,5,6連已經包4連)<br />\n<br />\n1234,2345,3456 各出現846次<br />\n846*3 = 2538<br />\n<br />\n咁之後再將2538 * 4!<br />\n因為要考慮我地用ctrl+f 冇搵到,佢地次序打亂左(例如1234變2341)既可能性<br />\n<br />\n咁即係60912<br />\n<br />\n最後結果就係60912/279936<br />\n<br />\n=0.2222222222<br />\n<br />\n睇落個機率都幾合理<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1623444唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話唔考慮次序呀嘛<br />\n咁你ctrl f咪miss咗呢啲</blockquote><br />\n1623444依種,用1234既數量乘左 4! 之後就包埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係(其實唔sure...)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4! 係包左1234自己排位咋嘛 例如係<br />\n1234555<br />\n1342555<br />\n4123555<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n但係唔會包左<br />\n1555234架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但乘7!既話個分子會大過個分母(岩岩發現我依個方法避唔到double counting問題,所以846依個數應該錯)<br />\n<br />\n1234555 之類係要 乘7! 除 3! 因為啲 5 係重覆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我再諗諗...</blockquote>"},{"pid":"bc441d99208b87c14f149ae5678abd7d3fa07797","tid":148173,"uid":45089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:33:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講返第1個問題<br />\n連number個度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuu.sh%2FuzJJf%2F42324964f6.csv&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a975b9d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://puu.sh/uzJJf/42324964f6.csv</a><br />\n首先呢,就用個excel檔列哂全部可能性(加埋有279936個)<br />\n<br />\n再ctrl+f 搜尋 1234, 2345, 3456 (4連既話得依3個可能性,5,6連已經包4連)<br />\n<br />\n1234,2345,3456 各出現846次<br />\n846*3 = 2538<br />\n<br />\n咁之後再將2538 * 4!<br />\n因為要考慮我地用ctrl+f 冇搵到,佢地次序打亂左(例如1234變2341)既可能性<br />\n<br />\n咁即係60912<br />\n<br />\n最後結果就係60912/279936<br />\n<br />\n=0.2222222222<br />\n<br />\n睇落個機率都幾合理<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1623444唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話唔考慮次序呀嘛<br />\n咁你ctrl f咪miss咗呢啲</blockquote><br />\n1623444依種,用1234既數量乘左 4! 之後就包埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係(其實唔sure...)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4! 係包左1234自己排位咋嘛 例如係<br />\n1234555<br />\n1342555<br />\n4123555<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n但係唔會包左<br />\n1555234架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但乘7!既話個分子會大過個分母(岩岩發現我依個方法避唔到double counting問題,所以846依個數應該錯)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1234555 之類係要 乘7! 除 3! 因為啲 5 係重覆</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我再諗諗...</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"eada128c18ce7cb0a9ff2d34dbd268712a1d68dc","tid":148173,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:50:03.000Z","msg":"計完，用inclusion-exclusion principle，<br />\n答案係107520/279936"},{"pid":"490574a78c4ec3369e24ef618293687ebd1740b3","tid":148173,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>計完，用inclusion-exclusion principle，<br />\n答案係107520/279936</blockquote><br />\n條數有D長，我簡略講下點做，想知Detail再問<br />\nLet <br />\nE1=Event of &quot;1&quot;exists，<br />\nE2=Event of &quot;2&quot;exist<br />\nand so on.<br />\n<br />\nLet<br />\nF1=E1 and E2 and E3 and E4<br />\nF2=E2 and E3 and E4 and E5<br />\nF3=E3 and E4 and E5 and E6<br />\n<br />\nWe want: F1 Or F2 Or F3<br />\nUsing I-E principle,<br />\n|U (F_i)| = |F1|+|F2|+|F3| - [|F1F2|+|F2F3|+|F3F1|] + [|F1F2F3|]<br />\nNote that, |F1|=|F2|=|F3|, |F1F2|=|F2F3|, |F3F1|=|F1F2F3|<br />\nSo, we only need |F1| and |F1F2|<br />\nand <br />\n|F1|=6^7-|~F1|<br />\nwhere |~F1|=|~E1 U ~E2 U ~E3 U ~E4|<br />\nBy I-E, we can find it.<br />\nSimilarly, we find <br />\n|F1|=57120 <br />\n|F1F2|=31920<br />\nand the result is 3*57120 - 2*31920=107520"},{"pid":"6a0cff2901e5c7560c7938be2c2c54e1b77fb798","tid":148173,"uid":24378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:03:30.000Z","msg":"會唔會係<br />\n4連：(5+5C2*2+5C3)*2+4+4C2*2+4C3<br />\n5連：(5+5C2)*2<br />\n6連：6<br />\n4連或以上：126<br />\n總可能組合數目：6+6C5*(5C2+5)+6C4*(4C3+4C2*2+4)+6C3*(3+3C2*3+3)+6C2*(6)+7=793<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n126/793？"},{"pid":"47f4b5a7684873797c443ed5307812c334ee9dcb","tid":148173,"uid":24378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係<br />\n4連：(5+5C2*2+5C3)*2+4+4C2*2+4C3<br />\n5連：(5+5C2)*2<br />\n6連：6<br />\n4連或以上：126<br />\n總可能組合數目：6+6C5*(5C2+5)+6C4*(4C3+4C2*2+4)+6C3*(3+3C2*3+3)+6C2*(6)+<span style=\"color: red;\">6</span>=<span style=\"color: red;\">792</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n126/792？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"16a080c5af642ef4948813d0545c8a3271731ef9","tid":148173,"uid":24378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:39:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://mathforum.org/library/drmath/view/56115.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmathforum.org%2Flibrary%2Fdrmath%2Fview%2F56115.html&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=1ef98a0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://mathforum.org/library/drmath/view/56115.html</a> 有個好好嘅方法計792出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 12!/(7!5!)"},{"pid":"490ce4bfa2f40cf16c509d1521264bf640d1e4ef","tid":148173,"uid":35829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>計完，用inclusion-exclusion principle，<br />\n答案係107520/279936</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我尋日係用dse雞方法去做 冇咁靚但係都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實同2014dse q19有異曲同工之妙<br />\ndse雞不妨入嚟挑戰一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e043538b7cb0fc7b6caf0a84bcebaaeb048d847","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>計完，用inclusion-exclusion principle，<br />\n答案係107520/279936</blockquote><br />\n條數有D長，我簡略講下點做，想知Detail再問<br />\nLet <br />\nE1=Event of &quot;1&quot;exists，<br />\nE2=Event of &quot;2&quot;exist<br />\nand so on.<br />\n<br />\nLet<br />\nF1=E1 and E2 and E3 and E4<br />\nF2=E2 and E3 and E4 and E5<br />\nF3=E3 and E4 and E5 and E6<br />\n<br />\nWe want: F1 Or F2 Or F3<br />\nUsing I-E principle,<br />\n|U (F_i)| = |F1|+|F2|+|F3| - [|F1F2|+|F2F3|+|F3F1|] + [|F1F2F3|]<br />\nNote that, |F1|=|F2|=|F3|, |F1F2|=|F2F3|, |F3F1|=|F1F2F3|<br />\nSo, we only need |F1| and |F1F2|<br />\nand <br />\n|F1|=6^7-|~F1|<br />\nwhere |~F1|=|~E1 U ~E2 U ~E3 U ~E4|<br />\nBy I-E, we can find it.<br />\nSimilarly, we find <br />\n|F1|=57120 <br />\n|F1F2|=31920<br />\nand the result is 3*57120 - 2*31920=107520</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac55eb9577e84de3a1ffae26a61b79af83c56cc6","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:36:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>計完，用inclusion-exclusion principle，<br />\n答案係107520/279936</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我尋日係用dse雞方法去做 冇咁靚但係都做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實同2014dse q19有異曲同工之妙<br />\ndse雞不妨入嚟挑戰一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ndse雞方法都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f2e0359bc16db347c96b10718ec71cfd341fe0","tid":148173,"uid":3258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T00:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://mathforum.org/library/drmath/view/56115.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmathforum.org%2Flibrary%2Fdrmath%2Fview%2F56115.html&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=1ef98a0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://mathforum.org/library/drmath/view/56115.html</a> 有個好好嘅方法計792出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 12!/(7!5!)</blockquote><br />\nsorry呀巴打<br />\n你依個ans好似同上面另一位巴打個0.3幾唔同<br />\n係咪少左d野?"}]}